RawQuestion: what type of government is the philippines?
ProcessedQuestion: what type of government is the philippines

Parses.Sparql:
PREFIX ns: <http://rdf.freebase.com/ns/>
SELECT DISTINCT ?x
WHERE {
FILTER (?x != ns:m.05v8c)
FILTER (!isLiteral(?x) OR lang(?x) = '' OR langMatches(lang(?x), 'en'))
ns:m.05v8c ns:location.country.form_of_government ?x .
}
